         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] (there is no grief, let alone) fear. [SKT] from pleasures (arises grief)</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] for those who are freed (from pleasures) [SKT] there is no (grief, let alone fear)</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] bitter are the things that delight</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] noble men say that that fetter is not strong</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] then the wise remove their lust</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] wavering are those who are desiring</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[SKT] then the realm of death does not come – that I say</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[TB] one should not be troubled by the mind</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
         <div type="comments">
            <p><note type="parallels"><bibl><title corresp="ref:bernhard1965"/><citedRange>112-114</citedRange></bibl>; <bibl><title corresp="ref:hahn2007"/><citedRange>17-18</citedRange></bibl></note><note corresp="#a1" type="philcomment">Uv.2.2d-3a <hi>nāsti śokaḥ kuto bhayam || 2 ratibhyo jāyate śokaḥ</hi></note><note corresp="#a2" type="philcomment">Uv.2.3c-d <hi>ratibhyo vipramuktānām nāsti śokaḥ kuto bhayam</hi></note><note corresp="#a3" type="philcomment">Uv.2.4b <hi>kaṭukā hy abhinanditāḥ</hi></note><note corresp="#a4" type="philcomment">Uv.2.5a <hi>na tad dṛḍhaṃ bandhanam āhur āryāḥ</hi></note><note corresp="#b1" type="philcomment">Uv.2.7d <hi>athātra dhīrā vinayanti cchandam</hi></note><note corresp="#b2" type="philcomment">Uv.2.8b <hi>santi tv anityāḥ kāmino yatra baddhāḥ</hi></note><note corresp="#b3" type="philcomment">Uv.2.8d <hi>hy anāgataṃ mṛtyudheyaṃ vadāmi</hi></note><note corresp="#b4" type="philcomment">Uv.2.9b <hi>manasānāvilo bhavet</hi></note></p>
